  <heading>LUTI6 (table, four registers, 8-bit)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Lookup table read with 6-bit indices (8-bit)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction copies indexed 8-bit elements from ZT0 to four destination
vectors using packed 6-bit indices in the three source vectors.
This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <uses_dit condition="FEAT_SVE2 is implemented or FEAT_SME is implemented">True</uses_dit>
    <sm_policy>SM_1_only</sm_policy>
  </desc>
  <operationalnotes>
